                            <comment id="12996114" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Thu, 17 Feb 2011 21:53:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The latest version of slf4j didn&apos;t seem to help the issue (but it prob makes sense to carry though and update to the latest version anyway)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The quickest resolution might be to patch zookeeper (esp since that is the way zookeeper is moving anyway).  A move to using log4j as the implementation for slf4j could be kept as a separate decision.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
